review.description:
My great-grandson attended this preschool in 2012 and 2013. He learned so much. The teachers are so dedicated and caring and the Director is great. The owner I also very kind. I needed a verification letter written and he very kindly did that for me within 48 hrs. My great-grandson is almost 8 yrs old and every time we drive by the preschool he says &quot; I wish I could go back there!&quot;
Wonderful experience!

Pam Morris
